Collections of useful programs and scripts


Programs in other directories
------------------------------

assemble.py                 assemble `zcom.h' from individual modules,
                            for internal use only
zcompick.py                 make `zcom.h' smaller by selecting only a few modules
                            independent of `assemble.py'
abpro/abemin.c              energy minimization program for AB protein model
python/cspacer/rstrip.py    remove trailing white spaces
python/cspacer/cspacer.py   add spaces to C code
python/cspacer/cindent.py   reformat leading indent for C code
python/pyembed/pyembed.py   embed python modules
python/gpload.py            load a gnuplot script
og/og.py                    object code generator
pdb/pdbalign/pdbalign.c     align two pdb structures
programs/netgrab/           grab/backup files on a server


Additional programs
--------------------
mkclean                     clean up common backup files


